recipes.name: French Fries
recipes.preparation: Peel and cut potatoes into sticks,Soak in cold water for half hour,Drain and pat dry,Fry in hot oil until golden brown,Season with salt and serve hot

recipes.name: Mango Juice
recipes.preparation: Peel and chop ripe mangoes, Put mango pieces in a blender,Add a bit of water,Add a bit of water,Pour into glasses and serve
